title: NFL ATL: Week 14 recap
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Week 14 recap
description:
A room full of heroes -- Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler Chris Wesseling and Kevin Patra -- recap all the Week 14 action including the “Sunday Night Football” matchup between the Carolina Panthers and New Orleans Saints. Don’t miss the key takeaways and analysis from each game. Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
